700784f-a.text:
College Avenue, east side, north from E. 145th to E.146th Streets, showing consecutively, St. Ritas Roman Cathalic Church, the rectory, and St. Ritas School. View 2 shows the church alone and views 3 and 4 the parochial school, view 4 being from
E. 146th Street.

NO REPROODUCTICNS  Views 1-4
